	<div class="intro"><p> <div class="bio"> <img src="_MG_9604.JPG" alt="bio photo of me" width="210" height="180"> </div> 
	Hi there, my name is April Qu. I am a recent business graduate with a concentration in marketing and a minor in psychology from Wilfrid Laurier University. I am a highly-organized, friendly and resourceful individual with over 1 year of office experience in administration and marketing. <br><br> I lived a year abroad and spent 6 months backpacking and volunteering across Europe. I am highly personable, multilingual in Mandarin and French, and comfortable engaging with different groups of people. I am passionate about travelling, discovering different cultures (and food!), and meeting new people. 
